"<%me>!": "We said we wouldn't do that! We promised each other!"
"Didn't we agree... There's no way we could leave each other behind!"
"Even if it causes history to unravel..."
"This can't be the end...! I won't... I will never, ever accept it!"
"It would deny history... The Akashic Record... A denial of my very existence."
"A world without <%me> must not be allowed!"
